# Scene.AnchorCollection.Iterator

**Type Alias**

An iterator that presents the elements of the collection.

## Declaration

```swift
typealias Iterator = Entity.ChildCollection.IndexingIterator<Scene.AnchorCollection>
```

## Iterating over the collection

- **makeIterator()**: Returns an iterator over the elements of the collection.
- **Scene.AnchorCollection.Element**: The type of element traversed by the iterator.
